ingredients
choped liver
salad
corriander
2 ripe tomatoes
1 tsp salt
1 onion ball

instructions
cut the tomatoes, onions and corriander separately
put the oil to boil for 60 seconds and add chopped onion
add the liver pieces and stir to mix
leave to cook for 5 minutes then add tomatoes and corriander
add salt and mix well


best served when hot
